snippet.title: TEDx636EleventhAve - Amber Chand - #healing
snippet.description:
Amber Chand, co-founder of Prosperity Candle, shares her journey from refugee to entrepreneur and a meditation on different ways to bring light into our lives.


About TEDx, x = independently organized event
In the spirit of ideas worth spreading, TEDx is a program of local, self-organized events that bring people together to share a TED-like experience. At a TEDx event, TEDTalks video and live speakers combine to spark deep discussion and connection in a small group. These local, self-organized events are branded TEDx, where x = independently organized TED event. The TED Conference provides general guidance for the TEDx program, but individual TEDx events are self-organized. (Subject to certain rules and regulations.)

snippet.title: Join SAMS & Amber Heard to Provide Care to Young Refugees
snippet.description: We recently met Weam, 12, on a medical mission to Jordan, alongside SAMS Goodwill Ambassador Amber Heard. We learned that Weam suffers from a life-threatening condition called Thalassemia, and she hasn't received the care that she needs in months due to budget cuts.
